Hotel Room Booking System

📌 Description

The Hotel Room Booking System is a Java-based application developed using JDBC to manage hotel room reservations. This project allows users to view available rooms, book rooms, and manage booking records efficiently.

It demonstrates how real-world hotel management systems handle customer bookings and room availability using a database.

🎯 Objective
To understand database connectivity using JDBC
To implement real-time booking functionality
To manage room availability and customer details
To build a practical backend project using Java
🛠️ Technologies Used
Java
JDBC (Java Database Connectivity)
MySQL / SQL Server
VS Code / Eclipse
MySQL Connector JAR
⚙️ Features
🛏️ View available rooms
📅 Book a room
❌ Cancel booking
📋 View booking details
🔍 Search booking by ID
🔄 Update booking information
